node.contents: I have Spring MVC application with connection to MySQL database. It runs on Tomcat server. I have a problem that the application doesn't respond after a few requests.

astNode.text: I have Spring MVC application with connection to MySQL database. It runs on Tomcat server. I have a problem that the application doesn't respond after a few requests.

node.contents: Case: I restart Tomcat server and open a page in a browser. The application runs and the server returns generated page to a browser. But when I open 5th-6th page in a browser, the server doesn't respond. Browser is still loading without no respond.
